    <summary>Installs the Alfen ACE Service Installer for servicing Alfen charging stations.</summary>

    <description>
### Alfen ACE Service Installer

This package installs **ACE Service Installer** from **Alfen**.  
ACE Service Installer is used by installers/service engineers to configure and service Alfen EV charging stations (NG platform).

#### Installation
- Downloads the official vendor MSI
- Installs silently using MSI (`/qn /norestart`)
- Verifies the download using a SHA256 checksum

#### Uninstallation
- Uninstalls silently using MSI (`msiexec /x {ProductCode}`)

Source MSI: https://knowledge.alfen.com/download/attachments/1627488257/ACE%20Service%20Installer%20v4.2.0_416.msi
    </description>

